  "transliteration": "niśhchayaṁ śhṛiṇu me tatra tyāge bharata-sattama\ntyāgo hi puruṣha-vyāghra tri-vidhaḥ samprakīrtitaḥ",
  "translation": "Hear My decisive conclusion about renunciation, O best of the Bharatas. Renunciation has been declared to be of three kinds.",
