  "chapter": 18,
  "verse": 69,
  "sanskrit": "न च तस्मान्मनुष्येषु कश्चिन्मे प्रियकृत्तम: |\nभविता न च मे तस्मादन्य: प्रियतरो भुवि ||",
  "transliteration": "na cha tasmān manuṣhyeṣhu kaśhchin me priya-kṛittamaḥ\nbhavitā na cha me tasmād anyaḥ priyataro bhuvi",
  "translation": "There is no one more dear to Me than such a person, nor will there ever be anyone more dear.",
